{
  "id": "RAW_5b92db70",
  "title": "一年狂赚 100 万！没人比 Polymarket 赌狗更懂 AI",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNTY1MjE2OA==&mid=2247492787&idx=1&sn=b34a52f3d29559fe409c182347b51988",
  "date": "2025-12-26 10:40:00",
  "author": "乌鸦智能说",
  "siteName": "乌鸦智能说",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a0ce96f7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2F9VjWVBpa4sz5qjvl9p3jx4t7HicFxqOjIpTLRp5qNX33tZnVjD1gaHibmoswpiaRh1xfVjTuth1V4R4aVdiacbwVXw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:0;margin-bottom:10px;text-align:center;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:unset;\">\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;line-height:1.75;\">\n      <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;caret-color: rgb(63, 63, 63);line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\">\n        <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n         <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\">\n          <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;line-height: 28px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n           <div style=\"padding:8.5px 17px;max-height:none;z-index:auto;background-size:auto;visibility:visible;bottom:auto;clear:none;line-height:29.75px;min-height:0px;border-color:rgb(63, 63, 63);background-position:0% center;float:none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;background-repeat:repeat;background-clip:border-box;top:auto;left:auto;border-width:0px;background-image:none;border-style:none;height:auto;min-width:0px;\">\n            <p><span leaf=\"\">如果非要选一群最懂AI动态的人，可能不是研究员，也不是分析师，而是Polymarket上的那帮赌徒。</span></p>\n            <p><span leaf=\"\">这里说的Polymarket，是一个国外的预测网站，在币圈火得一塌糊涂。</span></p>\n            <p><span leaf=\"\">在这个平台上，没有什么事情是不可以拿来开盘的：</span></p>\n            <p><span leaf=\"\">比特币价格能不能破15万？泰勒·斯威夫特会不会跟男朋友分手？甚至明年奥斯卡小金人发给谁？</span></p>\n            <p><span leaf=\"\">一句话，万物皆可赌，万物皆可搏。</span></p>\n            <p><span leaf=\"\">规则看上去门槛极低，谁都能上去押两把。但真正赚到钱的，始终是少数。</span></p>\n            <p><span leaf=\"\">Dune Analytics数据显示，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Polymarket上只有16.7%的用户是盈利的</span>。</span></p>\n            <p><span leaf=\"\">但就在这个充满了赌徒和尸体的修罗场里，硬生生杀出了一帮狠人。</span></p>\n            <p><span leaf=\"\">这帮人，专门靠预测AI 行业的事件赚钱。上到谷歌的新模型哪天发，下到 OpenAI 明年会不会出硬件。</span></p>\n            <p><span leaf=\"\">其中最猛的一个人，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">只用了一年时间，就靠预测AI行业的事件，赚了15万美元。换算成人民币，就是 100 多万</span>。</span></p>\n            <p><span leaf=\"\">于是，一个魔幻的现象出现了：</span></p>\n            <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">这个原本用来赌博的网站，硬生生被玩成了全球最准的AI情报中心</span>。而这帮下注的赌狗，却成了比华尔街分析师和科技媒体还懂AI的人。</span></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: unset;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;line-height:1.75;\">\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-size:15px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 19px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">/ 01 /</span></span></strong></span></strong></strong></span></strong></p>\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI</span><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 16px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: unset;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">赌神，齐聚Polymarket</span></strong></span></strong></span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">说起来，Polymarket的规则简单到令人发指，简单到连门口的保安大爷都能看懂：</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">每个问题只有两个选项：“YES”或者“NO”。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">价格在1美分到1美元之间波动，如果所有人觉得这事儿发生的概率有65%，那一份合约就卖0.65美元。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">一旦结果出来，赢家拿走1 美元，输家原地归零。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">如今，这个充满了赌徒和韭菜的修罗场，硬生生被玩成了全球最准的AI 情报中心，甚至你还会发现一个更魔幻的现象：</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">这帮赌狗，居然比华尔街分析师和科技媒体还懂AI。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">在Polymarket 上，最近杀出了一批靠预测 AI 动向赚钱的“大神”。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">其中最狠的一个老哥，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">叫</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">0xafEe</span>。</span></p>\n       <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100009127\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.23373493975903614\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"830\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=798c8882&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F9VjWVBpa4sz5qjvl9p3jx4t7HicFxqOjI6fNFriclDVFicSwGm9CibAlfsNEfNpxNGEzIsHP8DU9jCh3qTwOBQLRGg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">从去年12月到现在，只用了一年时间，0xafEe靠着预测赚了92万美元，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">光预测谷歌AI模型发布时间这事就赚了超过15万美元</span>。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">其中，赚得最多的AI预测是“Gemini 3.0会在10月31日之前发布吗？”，0xafEe以0.66美元的价格下注了“否”，一共买入了11.41万美元。</span></p>\n       <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100009128\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.44096385542168676\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"830\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3d55f5dd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F9VjWVBpa4sz5qjvl9p3jx4t7HicFxqOjI4s8FxMRczWc1gq8O8A4LdDOmvdOZHzIjmMicngMNSgLVf3yJoKzyKxg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">结果呢？Gemini 3.0 果然没发。光这一笔，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">0xafEe就赚走了5.81万美元</span>。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">进入11 月，这哥们更是杀疯了，先后押注了“Gemini 3.0 会在 11月 15 日之前发布吗？”、“Gemini 3.0 会在 11 月 22 日之前发布吗？”、“Gemini 3.0 会在 11 月 23 日之前发布吗？”。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">连续三把，虽然赔率不高，但架不住稳啊，又是6万美元落袋。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">更离谱的是，这哥们在“谷歌年度热搜词”的预测里，押注 23 次，中了 22 次。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">其中有一把，他花1 万多美金买了一个叫 d4vd 的超级冷门选项，当时市场概率只有0.2%，基本等于送钱。结果竟然中了，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">单笔获利近20万美金</span>。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">当然，盯着谷歌薅羊毛的不止他一个。还有个叫<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">ambuscade</span>的用户，也是个奇才。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">这人平时啥也不投，像个隐形人。在Gemini 3.0 Flash预测之外，其他预测寥寥，最多押注也不超过1000美元。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">但只要涉及到Gemini 3.0 Flash 的发布时间，他就像闻到了血腥味的鲨鱼。</span></p>\n       <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100009129\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.38313253012048193\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"830\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=94313025&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F9VjWVBpa4sz5qjvl9p3jx4t7HicFxqOjIVibs5KpwgIzEO1cGLn918XnsBPzu93raeAlc1DlH6RiagFpFYPiaUzs7g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">连续5次重金押注，无一失手，提走3万美元</span>。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">有网友扒出来，至少有4 个账号跟这帮人操作神同步。</span></p>\n       <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100009130\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.1177884615384615\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"832\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ea97bdc1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F9VjWVBpa4sz5qjvl9p3jx4t7HicFxqOjIaXV0c0WIoeKgyNAVtBTszzwzl7bg7NiagWQqxNg58aVfK3PSLl5xRpQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">平时装死，一到谷歌有动静，立马梭哈。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">谷歌这边漏成了筛子，OpenAI 那边也不遑多让。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">那边也有个“节奏大师”，这个人叫<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">pony-pony</span>（现更名yyds233）。<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">从今年8月到现在，他赚了8.45万美元</span>。</span></p>\n       <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100009131\" data-ratio=\"0.24519230769230768\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"832\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=54c7fe5e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F9VjWVBpa4sz5qjvl9p3jx4t7HicFxqOjIPGrMAhxofkOFYnwwW52VYIRicgum1O4WAcosicfQVqmSg2thngFcUbow%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">他只玩OpenAI 相关的盘口：新模型发不发？开源不开源？浏览器啥时候上？</span></p>\n       <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100009132\" data-ratio=\"0.5783132530120482\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"830\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2664024e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F9VjWVBpa4sz5qjvl9p3jx4t7HicFxqOjIlA4XBMhicxcHV64ppRZ193nSLforrkgLzdCuicX6QPTbJAGE9nkJBzxw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">命中率高得吓人。在数十次预测里，pony-pony只失手了5次，亏损也有限，剩下的全是精准狙击。</span></p>\n       <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100009133\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3349397590361446\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"830\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2d35136a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F9VjWVBpa4sz5qjvl9p3jx4t7HicFxqOjITXL5GurGogZNSGVbicZGmPJx5I6NhLW19cv0okialQ6hNsyWdWy5hbfw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">最神奇的是，亏损最多的一笔，极有可能还是自己故意输掉的。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">这事儿是这样的。由于这些人预测往往很准，因此也引来很多人跟风下注。为了把自己收益最大化，pony-pony就做了一个局。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">在预测”OpenAI是否会12月9日前发布新模型时“，他先是花300多美元以86%的概率价格押注了“Yes”，把市场情绪烘托起来，让韭菜们觉得“卧槽，大消息真要来了”。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">然后，在临近9 号的最后几个小时，趁着大家都在疯狂买 YES 的时候。他突然反手，大幅翻仓，全仓买入“NO”。</span></p>\n       <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100009134\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.06506024096385542\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"830\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5c78635d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F9VjWVBpa4sz5qjvl9p3jx4t7HicFxqOjIpNquIcwTJK6rxDWRmeibiasl25UDwSiagbuu6sVibb1A8DRbCN4msuHCJA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n       <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100009135\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07710843373493977\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"830\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2a8351dd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F9VjWVBpa4sz5qjvl9p3jx4t7HicFxqOjIZk17ibwbuzqZgBk2bwjCzII7xqJxqFvXF1FmZledcErX6UFSKCpMKng%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">最后，OpenAI果然“跳票”。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">一来一回，虽然前面亏了3000块的诱饵，但反手赚了 2.44万美元。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">回头看，Polymarket 之所以越来越准，并不是因为这里的人更聪明。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">而是因为在这里，信息被迫说真话。因为判断错了，是要真金白银买单的。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">所以你看到的，不是“赌狗变成了先知”，而是一个更残酷的事实：</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">当预测有成本，真相就会浮出来</span>。</span></p>\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-size:15px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 19px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">/ 02 /</span></span></strong></span></strong></strong></span></strong></p>\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI也开始下场收割了</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       <div>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">如果说上面那些赚了几十万美金的人类大神，让你觉得这就是赌博的巅峰。</span></p>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">那我只能说，兄弟，你格局小了。</span></p>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">在这个市场上，最恐怖的猎手，根本不是人，是AI。</span></p>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">当你还在那儿分析新闻、看推特、纠结要不要梭哈的时候，AI早就把全网信息扒了一遍，顺便把单子下了，甚至连你下单时手抖导致的那 0.01 秒延迟，都被它们吃干抹净了。</span></p>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">在这个修罗场里，AI 才是那个拿着加特林的终结者，而人类更像是那个拿着木棍的原始人。</span></p>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">现在Polymarket 上已经出现了两个堪称“赛博收割机”的神级AI账号。</span></p>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">第一个叫ilovecircle。这货简直就是个无情的赚钱机器。<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">短短两个月，通过全自动交易，狂赚220 万美元，胜率高达 74%</span>。</span></p>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">它是怎么做到的？</span></p>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">它挂载了神经网络，24 小时高强度监控全球互联网。新闻、财报、社交媒体情绪、甚至是链上的资金流向，全都在它的计算范围内。</span></p>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">比如“Gemini 3 到底发不发？”当你还在刷推特看爆料的时候，它可能已经监测到了谷歌某个 API 接口的变动，或者链上某笔大额资金的异常押注。</span></p>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">这种信息处理能力的差距，就是降维打击。</span></p>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">另一个大佬更恶心，叫SellLowBuyHigh（这名字就很搞事，高买低卖）。</span></p>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">它专门玩那种一两小时内结束的超短期盘口，比如“比特币 1 小时内会不会破 9 万”。</span></p>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">它的策略极其猥琐：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">捕捉平台赔率更新的延迟</span>。</span></p>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">你看到的价格，和系统实际成交的价格，中间可能有几百毫秒的误差。它就利用这个微小的缝隙，疯狂套利。</span></p>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">虽然每单赚得不多，但架不住它不用睡觉啊。靠着捡这些人类看不见的钢镚，它也硬生生捡出了12.4万美元。</span></p>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">这就是AI 的恐怖之处：它不仅比你聪明，还比你勤奋，最关键的是，它还没有因为亏钱而心率过速的毛病。</span></p>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">更夸张的是，这种“人机大战”已经不仅限于散户了。</span></p>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">现在，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">已经有家叫Event Trading Desk 的公司，专门搞了个 AI 交易平台</span>。</span></p>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">它们不猜涨跌，它们只算“合理价格”。</span></p>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">举个例子，如果AI 模型算出来某件事发生的概率是 60%，对应的价格应该是 0.6 美元。只要市场上的价格偏离了这个数，不管高了还是低了，AI 立马两边下注，锁定差价。</span></p>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">这叫什么？这叫“做市商”，也叫“庄家思维”。据说，这套策略的测试年化回报，能做到250%。</span></p>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">开源社区也没闲着。Polymarket Agents、Polyseer 这些AI代理“赌博”工具已经满天飞了。</span></p>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">摩根大通和德意志银行的试点显示，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">用AI增强的预测模型，准确率比传统方法高出30-50%</span>。</span></p>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">结合Polymarket与xAI的合作，AI每天能自动生成上百个新市场，未来AI驱动的预测模型可能会进一步放大这种信息差距，使专业玩家与普通用户之间的优势差更为明显。</span></p>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">信息差，正在被进一步放大。</span></p>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">作为一个既没有内幕，也没有算力的普通人。你盯着屏幕上跳动的数字，以为自己是在参与历史。</span></p>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">但到最后，在AI眼里，你更可能只是，那行代码里的一个微不足道的变量。</span></p>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">或者说，是代价。</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Polymarket 上的“AI 赌狗”和 AI 工具通过精准预测 AI 大厂动态赚取百万，揭示了信息在预测市场中“被迫说真话”的机制以及 AI 带来的“降维打击”效应。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Polymarket 上的“AI 赌狗”和 AI 工具通过精准预测 AI 大厂动态赚取百万，揭示了信息在预测市场中“被迫说真话”的机制以及 AI 带来的“降维打击”效应。",
  "summary": "本文深度剖析了 Polymarket 这一预测平台上的独特现象：一群被称为“赌狗”的用户和 AI 工具，通过精准预测 AI 行业动态（如谷歌和 OpenAI 的新模型发布时间），不仅赚取了巨额利润，更使得该平台演变为一个高效且准确的 AI 情报中心。文章详细介绍了 Polymarket 的运作机制，并通过 0xafEe 和 pony-pony 等“人类大神”的成功案例，展示了信息“被迫说真话”的机制如何让预测市场变得高效。更进一步，文章揭示了 AI 在 Polymarket 上的“降维打击”效应，例如 ilovecircle 和 SellLowBuyHigh 这类 AI 账户如何通过全自动交易、高速信息处理和捕捉市场延迟实现超额收益。最后，文章探讨了这种人机协作和竞争模式下，信息差被进一步放大的趋势，以及普通用户在 AI 驱动的预测市场中可能面临的挑战和地位。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Polymarket 通过其独特的市场机制，将预测转化为可交易合约，使得信息“被迫说真话”。",
      "explanation": "在这个平台进行预测有真金白银的代价，从而促使参与者更严谨地分析信息，最终使其成为一个高度准确的 AI 信息预测平台，甚至超越传统分析师和媒体。"
    },
    {
      "point": "“AI 赌狗”通过挖掘和分析科技巨头（如谷歌、OpenAI）的公开及非公开信息，精准预测新产品发布等关键事件。",
      "explanation": "文章以具体案例（0xafEe 预测 Gemini 发布、pony-pony 预测 OpenAI 动态）展示了这些顶尖的个人玩家如何利用高超的信息分析能力和策略性下注赚取巨额利润，甚至利用信息差进行“做局”操纵市场。"
